s/foreign-direct-investment-in-ireland-june-2023/">最大挑战</a>，而过度拥挤可能是反移民政治最终席卷爱尔兰的原因之一。如果这个问题得不到解决，爱尔兰可能会追随<a href="https://worksinprogress.co/issue/why-britain-doesnt-build">英国的脚步陷入优雅的衰落</a>并非不可想象。</p><p>但就目前而言，爱尔兰仍然对凯尔特老虎时代的成功感到自豪。一个曾经被邻国征服和<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anti-Irish_sentiment">蔑视的</a>国家现在成为财富和高科技技能的灯塔。</p><p>我认为这给我们上了关于国家发展的重要一课。如果你回到 1923 年，问人们一百年后爱尔兰是否会比英国更富有，你认为有多少人会回答“是”？有多少人会当面嘲笑你？然而一个世纪后，我们却来到了这里，这就是现实。现在拿出一张世界地图，选出一些大多数人认为不具备致富条件的国家。您认为 100 年后这些国家会在哪里？</p><p>你确定吗？ </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-ireland-got-so-rich?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-ireland-got-so-rich?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p>PS - 这里有一些我在基尔肯尼随机拍摄的（未经编辑的）照片……大多数只是标准的“古老城堡和绿色乡村”的东西，但有几张展示了小市中心的样子。 </p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ec7821b6-13b3-4e10-a595-3d04f16b22f4_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/aafa4108-346c-4cc7-bbb9-3b2058aff440_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7053d0ab-b00c-4511-b36a-aa07cde0c9a7_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3316b253-58ef-41cb-a8fd-9e0f7a990a69_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/765c82cd-6a44-49be-9116-6d4c50c45a44_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2cd38326-05c8-49a7-b2ff-2227bebed161_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4706cd06-79b1-4a2a-bce6-51ea703146b5_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/57766198-90c0-4f1e-92e2-be3054820de4_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/598f23ab-831b-46df-bad3-951aed1befd4_3072x4080.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/11cef507-7628-4535-91a0-d2a3705b3c22_1456x1454.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div> ; 
The Middle East is getting olderWhy I'm optimistic about the waning of conflict in the region. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-middle-east-is-getting-older https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-middle-east-is-getting-olderNoah Smith Sun, 05 Nov 2023 02:16:18 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg" width="1024" height="768" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:768,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:519992,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb81d5631-8923-424a-a9f4-4ec2afec560a_1024x768.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">作者： <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=17138401">Syria-Frames-Of-Freedom</a> （支持 FSA 的信息）- [1]，CC BY 2.0</figcaption></figure></div><p>我注意到以色列-加沙战争中一些有趣的事情似乎普遍被忽视了：战争并没有显示出太多蔓延到整个中东的迹象。也门胡塞武装（伊朗的傀儡民兵组织之一）向以色列的大致方向发射了几枚导弹，并<a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/features/2023/11/2/analysis-houthis-declare-war-on-israel-but-their-real-target-is-elsewhere">大声宣战</a>，但似乎没有人很担心。 2006年，黎巴嫩民兵真主党与以色列的战斗陷入僵局，但现在<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/world-news/2023/11/03/hassan-nasrallah-hezbollah-speech-oct-7-hamas-iran-israel/">它选择不介入</a>这场冲突，伊朗本身也是如此。早在2000年代初期，每个人都害怕的“阿拉伯街道”肯定有支持巴勒斯坦人的抗议活动，但<a href="https://carnegieendowment.org/2023/11/01/pay-attention-to-arab-public-response-to-israel-hamas-war-pub-90893">他们一直非常和平</a>。沙特阿拉伯表示，<a href="https://www.axios.com/2023/10/31/saudi-megadeal-normalization-israel-biden">仍希望与以色列实现关系正常化</a>，但以停火为条件。</p><p>这是一个非常好的迹象，与战争最初几天大家所抱有的可怕期望相去甚远。 2011年，“阿拉伯之春”如野火般蔓延，引发了叙利亚和也门大规模、漫长的血腥战争，以及整个中东地区的各种小规模战争；以色列-加沙战争没有任何迹象表明这段历史会重演。</p><p>当然，这可能有很多原因。经过二十年的战争，该地区可能已经筋疲力尽。<a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/news/two-navy-aircraft-carriers-mediterranean/">美国的威慑</a>可能正在限制伊朗及其代理人的手。对于该地区来说，以巴冲突可能根本不如伊朗和沙特阿拉伯之间的长期冷战那么重要。 ETC。</p><p>但我认为人口老龄化也可能与此有关。有相当成熟的文献将年轻人口膨胀与冲突风险升高联系起来。当然，这种联系只是一种相关性——除了战争本身之外，显然很难找到改变一个国家年龄结构的自然实验。但这是一个相当明确的相关性。例如， <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-73065-9_3">Cincotta 和 Weber (2021)</a>发现，年龄中位数为 25 岁或以下的国家更有可能发生革命： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg" width="668" height="460.16157205240177" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:631,&quot;width&quot;:916,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:668,&quot;bytes&quot;:79076,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1601c66b-4679-47c9-a808-c2ed2afea164_916x631.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-030-73065-9_3">Cincotta 和 Weber (2021)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p> <a href="https://academic.oup.com/isq/article/50/3/607/1800827?login=false">Urdal (2006)</a>发现：</p><blockquote><p>人们经常认为……所谓的“青年膨胀”使国家更容易受到政治暴力的影响……这一说法在 1950 年至 2000 年期间国内武装冲突的时间序列跨国统计模型中得到了实证检验，以及 1984-1995 年恐怖主义和骚乱的事件数据。所有三种形式的暴力都强烈支持年轻人激增会增加政治暴力风险的预期。</p></blockquote><p><a href="https://www.cfr.org/report/family-planning-strategic-focus-us-foreign-policy">马德森（2021）</a>写道：</p><blockquote><p> 20 世纪 90 年代的证据表明，15 岁至 29 岁人口占成年人口 40% 以上的国家，遭受内战的可能性是其他国家的两倍。 1970 年至 2007 年间，80% 的国内冲突爆发发生在至少 60% 的人口年龄在 30 岁以下的国家……这些国家中只有少数国家被评为民主国家，并且对政治自由、腐败和政治自由的限制。机构能力薄弱也很常见。从 1950 年到 2000 年收集的数据发现，那些 35% 或以上成年人口由 15 岁到 24 岁的人组成的国家，爆发内战的可能性要高出 150%。在生育率持续较高的国家，这种相关性最强。一旦人口转变完全开始，尽管由于过去高生育率带来的人口动力，人口仍然年轻，但爆发冲突的可能性较小。</p></blockquote><p> <a href="https://erf.org.eg/app/uploads/2019/06/1310.pdf">Ibrahim (2019)</a>和其他人也发现了类似的结果。一如既往，<a href="https://www.newsecuritybeat.org/2018/04/age-structure-intra-state-conflict-imagined/">该理论存在批评者</a>，一些作者根据不同类型的冲突进行了区分——例如， <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Dan-Miodownik/publication/265650970_Youth_bulge_and_civil_war_Why_a_country's_share_of_young_adults_explains_only_non-ethnic_wars/links/5ad50cf9a6fdcc2935809baa/Youth-bulge-and-civil-war-Why-a-countrys-share-of-young-adults-explains-only-non-ethnic-wars.pdf">Yair 和 Midownik (2014)</a>声称青年膨胀与“种族战争”不太相关，而 Cincotta 和 Weber (2021) ）警告说，他们的结果更难测试“分裂主义”战争。但无论如何，该领域的普遍共识似乎是，非常年轻的人口与不稳定和暴力有关。</p><p>关于为何青年人激增可能引发冲突，有多种理论。资源稀缺是非常贫穷国家的一个明显因素。在其他国家，有一种理论认为，年轻人的激增会导致年轻人的经济和社会机会减少——基本上，年轻人互相排挤，这让他们生气。当经济停滞时，这种效应显然会加剧。此外，身边有很多年轻人而没有什么可失去的，这本身就是一个风险因素。</p><p>中东停滞的经济显然是席卷整个地区的暴力事件的一个因素（当然，这显然是双向的因果关系）。无论富裕还是贫穷，大中东地区的国家——我会把阿富汗和巴基斯坦也包括在内，因为它们也是冲突的重灾区——就是根本不会经历太多的经济增长。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg" width="684" height="490.8705882352941" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/48c079cd-0411-42ee-b82e-3254f6c648ce_1020x732.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermar