s&quot;:418244,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F13f69f8a-966e-4534-8957-770bb4166995_1601x1221.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://howmuch.net/articles/us-exports-imports-trade-balance">HowMuch.net</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>由于南亚和东南亚的快速增长，即使我们继续与中国脱钩，该地区对美国经济的重要性<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-next-phase-of-globalization-is">也只会增加</a>。</p><p>与此同时，中东作为贸易伙伴绝对很小。特别是，美国根本不依赖中东石油。由于水力压裂，我们成为<a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-poised-become-net-exporter-crude-oil-2023-2022-12-19/">原油净出口国</a>。沙特阿拉伯、阿联酋和科威特可能会被哥斯拉吃掉，而我们的炼油厂将继续运转。 （顺便说一句，拜登领导下的美国石油产量<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/08/09/business/oil-production-biden-trump/index.html">刚刚创下新纪录</a>。）</p><p>现在，我们的一些盟友，比如日本和韩国，确实仍然购买了大量中东石油。如果中东石油供应出现严重中断，全球石油价格将大幅上涨，为美国石油生产商带来意外之财，但也会损害其他类型的美国企业。但<a href="https://about.bnef.com/blog/electric-cars-have-dented-fuel-demand-by-2040-theyll-slash-it/">由于电动汽车的兴起</a>，石油对全球经济的重要性日益降低。预计石油总消耗量很快就会持平。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F919d331b-55ab-4cca-8109-f826f84c697f_655x398.jpeg" width="655" he